reviewText: I should have read the reviews first!  My first record (I was 5 yo) was of the theme song, and not one of these episodes has it.  There were only 26 episodes...you'd think they could have included one episode with the song.
Loved this show when I was a kid. Purchased mainly to listen to the theme song "Champion the Wonder Horse" sung by Frankie Lang. It is not there. Terribly disappointed.
I love Movies. I choose them on seeing them.  I love the packaging.  I use to watch these on tv at home when I was a little girl
